cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CR 

The paper focuses on using deep Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) for human pose estimation to recognize the intentions of vulnerable road users (VRUs) such as pedestrians and cyclists. This involves computer vision and robotics (cs.CV, cs.RO), as well as machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI, cs.LG). Additionally, the paper addresses the issue of safety and security in autonomous driving, which falls under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR).
